  "instructions": [
    "Mix yogurt with red pepper flakes, turmeric powder, ginger paste, garlic paste, coconut milk, cumin powder, coriander powder, sesame seeds, and paprika in a bowl.",
    "Heat olive oil in an air fryer basket until hot. Carefully add the yogurt mixture to the hot air fryer.",
    "Air fry at 375°F for about 10-12 minutes or until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Drizzle with extra olive oil if needed, then serve immediately."
